give url to local only in xampp
in xampp/apache/config/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf



<VirtualHost *:8080>
   
    DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs"
    ServerName localhost
    
</VirtualHost>

dont user .dev , .com 

<VirtualHost *:8080>
  
    DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs/public/"
    ServerName blog.test
    
</VirtualHost>

Save

Next open as adminstator empty notepad
file/open/c://system32/driver/etc/hosts   file

add to theing
127.0.0.1 localhost
127.0.0.1 blog.test
s
save 
and restart the xampp apache start stop


